Alice and Martin;;48;;61;;R;;Twenty-year-old Frenchman Martin (Alexis Loret) seems to be living the dream. After moving from the French countryside to Paris, he quickly found professional success as a fashion model and romantic fulfillment in dating his half brother's fiery roommate, Alice (Juliette Binoche). Deep down, however, he is avoiding inner turmoil that stems from his tumultuous upbringing. But when Alice becomes unexpectedly pregnant, the full force of his repression is let loose, wreaking havoc on his life.;;Drama;;André Téchiné;;1998;;Juliette Binoche,Alexis Loret,Carmen Maura,Mathieu Amalric,Pierre Maguelon,Jeremy Kreikenmeyer;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alice_et_martin